<p>
<lb n="1"/>[[ma]]rāna t<unclear>i</unclear>r<unclear>i</unclear>puvanac cakkaravatt<unclear>ikaḷ</unclear><hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>
<lb n="2"/>ti[[nnāṟā]]vatu kunṟakkūṟṟamāna Uttoṅka
<lb n="3"/>[[ṭa]] Iccuramuṭaiyār koyilil kāṇi Uṭaiya civa
<lb n="4"/><unclear>U</unclear>ḷḷi<unclear>tā</unclear>rum nāṭṭān cokkanāna tillai<unclear>nā</unclear>yaka
<lb n="5"/>[[ṭā]]n tiricciṟṟampalamuṭaiyān panmāye<unclear>ccu</unclear>
<lb n="6"/>[[v]]āṇan parameccura paṭṭan Uḷḷiṭṭārum muppa
</p>

